summary: This document contains the Articles of Organization for NES, LLC, filed with the New York Department of State. It outlines the formation details of the limited liability company, including its name, location, and the authority of its members. The document is dated August 12, 1998, and includes filing receipts and associated fees.

persons.name: Lauren Kwintner
persons.context: Lauren Kwintner is mentioned as the filing agent for NES, LLC, responsible for submitting the Articles of Organization.

events.title: Formation of NES, LLC
events.description: The Articles of Organization for NES, LLC were filed with the New York Department of State.

keyFacts: The document outlines the formation of NES, LLC under New York Limited Liability Company Law.
The filing was executed on August 12, 1998.
Lauren Kwintner is identified as the filing agent for the company.
The company is located in New York County.
The document includes details about the authority of the members and the registered agent for process.
